high_descs: Walk to the tomato on the sink.
Pick up the tomato on the sink.
Turn right and walk to the table in the opposite corner of the room.
Place the tomato on the table.
Pick up the knife in front of the pot on the table.
Cut up the tomato on the table.
Place the knife in front of the pot on the table.
Pick up a piece of tomato from the table.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Chill the piece of tomato in the fridge and then pick up the piece of tomato from the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the table with the blue plates on it.
Place the piece of tomato to the right of the cut up tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a piece of chilled tomato on the table across from the fridge.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the kitchen sink.
Pick up the tomato from the drying rack in the left side of the sink.
Carry the tomato to the white table in the corner of the room.
Place the tomato on the table between the butter knife and the rightmost blue plate.
Pick up the butter knife from the table.
Use the knife to slice the tomato on the table.
Place the butter knife back on the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Carry the slice of tomato to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the tomato on the shelf to the right of the blue plate, close the door, wait a few seconds, and then remove it from the fridge.
Turn and carry the tomato back to the kitchen table.
Place the slice on the table up against the left side of the rightmost blue plate.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled slice of tomato to the kitchen table.

high_descs: Walk to the sink.
Pick up the tomato.
Turn right, walk to the fridge, turn right, and walk to the table.
Put the tomato on the table.
Pick up the knife.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Pick up a tomato slice.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the tomato slice in the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge, pick up the tomato slice, and close the fridge.
Walk back to the table.
Put the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold tomato slice on the table.
